1
00:00:00,125 --> 00:00:01,959
Unogona kunge wakanzwa nezveBhuku raMormoni,

2
00:00:01,959 --> 00:00:04,542
asi ungangoshamisika nezvarinotaura
pamusoro pazvo chaizvo.

3
00:00:04,542 --> 00:00:05,417
Nechepamusoro,

4
00:00:05,417 --> 00:00:08,542
irondedzero yechiuru
chemakore yerudzi rukuru.

5
00:00:08,542 --> 00:00:09,501
Asi pachokwadi,

6
00:00:09,501 --> 00:00:14,542
riri pamusoro pevanhu varikuedza kudzidza
nezvaJesu Kristu uye kumutevera.

7
00:00:14,542 --> 00:00:18,209
Rinotangira muJerusarema munana 600
Kristu Asati Azvarwa apo muporofita

8
00:00:18,209 --> 00:00:21,417
paakayambirwa naMwari kutiza
ruparadzo rweguta urwo rwaiuya.

9
00:00:21,417 --> 00:00:23,459
Iye nemhuri yake vanotungamirirwa mhiri

10
00:00:23,459 --> 00:00:26,000
kwegungwa kunzvimbo yava
iyezvino maAmerica. ​

11
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:28,667
Vanhu vacho vanowanda uye
pokupedzisira vanokamuka

12
00:00:28,667 --> 00:00:31,667
kuva ndudzi huru mbiri dzine
nguva dzehondo norugare.

13
00:00:31,667 --> 00:00:35,584
​Upenyu hwavo hunokwanisa kukukurudzira
kuva nerutendo munaJesu Kristu,

14
00:00:35,584 --> 00:00:38,250
kuchengeta mirairo Yake,
uye kushandira vamwe.

15
00:00:38,250 --> 00:00:40,959
Bhuku raMormoni rine
mashoko matsvene evaporofita

16
00:00:40,959 --> 00:00:43,250
avo vakapupura nezvekuuya kweMuponesi.

17
00:00:43,250 --> 00:00:46,042
Rinosimbisa zvokwadi
zveBhaibheri uye rinopupura

18
00:00:46,042 --> 00:00:48,667
kuti Jesu Kristu ndiye Mwanakomana waMwari;

19
00:00:48,667 --> 00:00:50,042
kuti Akararama, akafa,

20
00:00:50,042 --> 00:00:53,542
uye akakunda rufu nezvivi
kuitira mumwe nemumwe wedu.

21
00:00:53,542 --> 00:00:57,083
Ndikokusaka richinzi “Imwe
Testamente yaJesu Kristu.”

22
00:00:57,083 --> 00:00:57,709
Pachokwadi,

23
00:00:57,709 --> 00:01:01,792
chiitiko chinokoshesesa chebhuku
racho ndeche kushanya kwaJesu Kristu

24
00:01:01,792 --> 00:01:05,667
kuvanhu mumaAmerica mushure mekumuka
kuvakafa Kwake muJerusarema.

25
00:01:05,667 --> 00:01:08,459
Anodzidzisa vhangeri Rake,
anoporesa vanorwara,

26
00:01:08,459 --> 00:01:10,125
uye anoropafadza vana vavo.

27
00:01:10,125 --> 00:01:12,751
Asi uku kunongova kutanga kwenyaya yacho.

28
00:01:12,751 --> 00:01:16,042
Shanduro chaiyo yeBhuku
raMormoni ndeye makwanisiro

29
00:01:16,042 --> 00:01:19,792
arinoita kubatsira nezvinetso
zvaunotarisana nazvo nhasi.

30
00:01:19,792 --> 00:01:22,292
Unokwanisa kuwana nyaradzo, nhungamiro,

31
00:01:22,292 --> 00:01:25,709
nekudzidza kuva munhu ari
nani uye anonyanya kufara.

32
00:01:25,709 --> 00:01:26,334
Chikurusa,

33
00:01:26,334 --> 00:01:30,083
unokwanisa kuswedera pedyo
neMuponesi wako Jesu Kristu.

